body_html:
I had this issue when using an aws instance that had tensorflow installed.
I tried installing mock, but it didn't make any change.
Finally, it turned out the installed tensorflow version was quite old and the issue was related to this tensorflow/serving#139

I just had to upgrade tensorflow and it worked: https://www.tensorflow.org/get_started/os_setup

body:
I had this issue when using an aws instance that had tensorflow installed.
I tried installing mock, but it didn't make any change.
Finally, it turned out the installed tensorflow version was quite old and the issue was related to this https://github.com/tensorflow/serving/issues/139

I just had to upgrade tensorflow and it worked: https://www.tensorflow.org/get_started/os_setup
